        {
          "id": "speaker-encoder",
          "title": "Speaker encoder：mel 到 embedding",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Qwen3TTSSpeakerEncoder 是 ECAPA 风格说话人编码器。配置类的 extraction contract 默认 sample_rate=24000、mel_dim=128，模型 forward 产出 speaker embedding；这里组合的是配置与静态张量契约，不声称音频已在本机执行。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-001", "TGT-CONFIG-001"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-001", "TGT-CONFIG-001"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "talker",
          "title": "Talker：text+codec 到 codec-0",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Qwen3TTSTalkerForConditionalGeneration 把文本与已有 codec 条件送入 decoder，并由 LM head 预测 codec-0 logits。codec-0 是 Talker 的主序列输出，不能与后续残差码本组混为一谈。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-002"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-002"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "code-predictor",
          "title": "MTP：由配置决定的残差码本",
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "训练 helper forward_sub_talker_finetune 读取 Talker hidden state 与 codec_ids，构造子 Talker 输入后调用 code_predictor.forward_finetune，并返回 logits 与 residual-codebook loss；它不属于 runtime inference chain。",
              "state": "verified",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-004", "TGT-MODEL-002"]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "静态公式是 residual groups = num_code_groups - 1；配置类默认值为 32，但实际发布 checkpoint 配置 pending，当前固定 evidence 没有锁定其真实 num_code_groups，因此不把默认值换算成发布模型结论。",
              "state": "inference",
              "evidence_ids": ["TGT-CONFIG-001", "TGT-MODEL-002"]
            },
            {"type": "source_refs", "evidence_ids": ["TGT-MODEL-004", "TGT-MODEL-002"]}
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "precision-islands",
          "title": "目标源码的 FP32 精度岛",
          "blocks": [
